{
  "stem": "11075.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and then-- then in the same day, was liquidation, you know, the whole ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They took, you know, all the rest people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My mother, my two sisters, myself, and the little baby, they took, you know, to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Over there was a-- we were over there a nice couple hours.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we came over there, with us first, maybe about-- about 3,000 without food, without water.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we came over there, wagons were already prepared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and so just the young men they took out, you know, from the group.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they sent-- they send-- and they sent us away to [INAUDIBLE]-- to-- to Stalowa Wola.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Stalowa Wola-- that's in Poland, a steel factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all the rest, you know, went into the black wagons, you know, and send to Chelmno.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To Chelmno, to death.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So we-- I came to-- to Stalowa Wola.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No food and not water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because when we came over there, when we came to Stalowa Wola-- was-- not only from Wolbrom, you know, but it was from other-- other cities, also.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From small cities was also there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was all together, maybe between 9,000 and 10,000.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the SS men, every night-- he walked like-- like he walked on a carpet-- killed about 10, 15 people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we get up in the morning, about 10, 15 people were dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what happened every night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean in Stalowa Wola.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stalowa Wola was a factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we walked five miles-- five kilometers-- every day, each way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we came over there, we worked, you know, like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It-- it-- it very-- labor-- labor work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Labor work in the factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they-- and they made steel.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
